Error.Message:
EvalutionE:1~11,EvalutionH:1~11,EvalutionR:1~11
抽象類別只需要一個，且子類別的物件資料不應出現在父類別。
public abstract class Evalution {
    protected String sid,name,grade,proportion; 
    public Evalution(String s,String n,String g,String p) {
        this.sid = s;
        this.name = n;
        this.grade = g;
        this.proportion =p;      
    }
}

Exam:3~3,Homework:3~3,Homework:3~3
super內參數改寫與父類別一致
super ( s , n , g , p ) ;

